Aerospace Show China ' 98 Opens in Zhuhai
ZHUHAI , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- The Second China International Aviation and Aerospace Exhibition , or the Aerospace Show China ' 98 , today opened in south China city of Zhuhai .
Li Peng , chairman of the Standing Committee of National People 's Congress , declared the opening of the event .
Vice-Premier Wu Bangguo made a speech at today 's opening ceremony , which was also attended by Zhang Wannian , Vice-chairman of the Central Military Commission .
More than 500 companies from 22 countries and regions have been represented at the show .
Pilots from China and Russia performed stunt flights at the ceremony .
By press time , the stunt flights are still going on .
